== Description ==
Test the upgrade of oVirt Hosted Engine deployments

== Setup ==
# Deploy Hosted Engine on a clean system using a previous stable release ensuring to have the same oVirt version both on hosts and Hosted Engine VM. 

==How to test==
# Ensure Hosted Engine is working
# Follow [[Hosted_Engine_Howto#Upgrade_Hosted_Engine | Upgrade Hosted Engine]] guide
# Ensure Hosted Engine is still working after the upgrade

==Expected Results==
* The Hosted Engine upgrade is completed without errors
* The Hosted Engine deployment is still working after the upgrade

==Optional==
* Perform other oVirt Hosted Engine / oVirt Engine test cases

